10
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:13,000
This pure is not the clean or dirty pure.

11
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:20,000
It's just naturally, it's already pure in its own essence, never been contaminated before.

12
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,000
You think you have all these wandering thoughts. Actually, you don't.

13
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:29,000
