14
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:32,000
Usually, we have the metaphor of a mirror.

15
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:36,000
It's never affected by whatever comes and goes.

16
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Nothing really affected you. You're always perfect and complete and pure.

17
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:47,000
Your true self really has no wandering thought at all. Just know that for a fact.

18
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,000
So that's the first one.

19
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:54,000
The second one is the self-nature does not arise or perish.

20
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:58,000
Everything in life is based on cause and control.

21
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:03,000
Everything comes and goes because there's a cause.

22
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:09,000
