25
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:19,000
That's the same as our lives. We have our birth, life, and then we have our death.

26
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,000
Everything is coming and going.

27
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:28,000
But there's only one thing that doesn't perish if your body dies.

28
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:31,000
And what is that? Your self-nature.

29
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:36,000
It never got started or ended. There's no beginning and there's no ending.

30
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,000
It will continue no matter what happens to you.

31
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Your self-nature will go on forever and ever.

32
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:49,000
So know this for a fact and not be afraid of anything that happens in life or death or anything.

33
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:54,000
